00:26:55,589 --> 00:26:57,790
So this is what hallways used to look like in the game.

583
00:26:58,470 --> 00:26:59,531
And this had a lot of problems.

584
00:26:59,591 --> 00:27:01,992
Basically, because you can change gravity, we have

