610
00:27:57,206 --> 00:27:58,927
So you can see it, you know,

611
00:27:58,947 --> 00:28:00,408
it touches the end of the hallway.

612
00:28:00,428 --> 00:28:02,089
And this immediately solved a ton of problems.

613
00:28:02,129 --> 00:28:04,171
So now when you open the door

614
00:28:04,391 --> 00:28:05,411
and you're looking down a hallway,

615
00:28:05,471 --> 00:28:07,793
you see the brightest thing on the screen is the window,

616
00:28:07,853 --> 00:28:10,374
right, and the window offers a vista to the outside world,

617
00:28:10,394 --> 00:28:12,435
which is much more interesting than the blank walls.

618
00:28:12,815 --> 00:28:14,516
So it actually makes traversal through hallways

619
00:28:14,556 --> 00:28:15,417
feel a lot faster.

620
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:18,300
and it attracts people towards the end.

621
00:28:18,881 --> 00:28:21,622
And then the window kind of guides your eyes

622
00:28:21,762 --> 00:28:22,882
into the direction of the bend.

623
00:28:23,222 --> 00:28:25,523
And this solves the problem of hallways that bend upwards

624
00:28:25,543 --> 00:28:28,245
because now players' eyes are guided to look up.

625
00:28:28,825 --> 00:28:31,306
And it also solves the problem of players going backwards

626
00:28:31,366 --> 00:28:32,646
because now when you're going backwards,

627
00:28:32,686 --> 00:28:34,107
the hallway looks very different.

628
00:28:34,147 --> 00:28:36,928
You're no longer seeing this window of light at the end.

629
00:28:37,308 --> 00:28:40,069
So just the way the hallways are designed,

630
00:28:40,229 --> 00:28:42,050
you can figure out the direction you're supposed to go.

631
00:28:42,610 --> 00:28:43,531
And I actually, you know,

632
00:28:44,371 --> 00:28:49,014
sometimes in games they'll want to vary corners and hallways.

633
00:28:49,054 --> 00:28:51,215
And I actually have this in every single hallway because

634
00:28:51,635 --> 00:28:54,517
having the player get lost inside hallways is not

635
00:28:54,537 --> 00:28:59,279
something that I want to do. So in summary, you want to

636
00:28:59,319 --> 00:29:02,301
