637
00:29:02,361 --> 00:29:04,742
using impossible geometry you're going to find unexpected

638
00:29:04,782 --> 00:29:08,264
solutions to previous problems. You will need to rethink a lot

639
00:29:08,284 --> 00:29:09,065
