640
00:29:09,758 --> 00:29:12,699
You'll need to rethink direction, northeast, southwest,

641
00:29:13,019 --> 00:29:15,160
up, down, left, right, those all go out the window.

642
00:29:16,600 --> 00:29:19,921
Utilize a very clear layout for your level.

643
00:29:19,941 --> 00:29:22,182
The shape of it should be easily recognizable.

644
00:29:22,762 --> 00:29:24,223
You want to create logic in your level

645
00:29:24,303 --> 00:29:27,644
so the players can figure out where they need to go next

646
00:29:27,684 --> 00:29:28,764
by looking at the architecture.

647
00:29:30,003 --> 00:29:31,663
and you also want to have intentional architecture.

648
00:29:31,683 --> 00:29:33,364
Everything you put in the game needs to tell the player

649
00:29:33,704 --> 00:29:36,525
how to use it, and use established patterns

650
00:29:36,545 --> 00:29:37,905
that the players can rely on

651
00:29:38,265 --> 00:29:39,305
to figure out where they need to go.

